      <ReleaseDate>2022-07-26T09:56:13Z</ReleaseDate>
      <Description>This  dataset contains magnetic field components  from GEOS-2 S-300 wave experiment (search coil magnetometer) given in SRV Coordinate System in nT. Time resolution is 43 ms. The data format is RFF (Roproc File Format ftp://ftp.lpp.polytechnique.fr/robert/keep/Biblio_et_CV/Working_documents/2015_Robert_The_Roproc_File_Format_V2p3.pdf)

    Bx, By, Bz: Magnetic field
    Dx, Dy: despin signals corresponding to the continuous magnetic field rotation</Description>
